      "literal": "This unit group covers handicraft workers who perform traditional handicrafts not classified elsewhere. For instance, the group includes traditional handicraft workers in non-precious metals and stone.\nExamples of the occupations classified here:\n- Candle-maker (handicraft)\n- Metal toymaker\n- Stone articles handicraft worker\n",
